propertyObj.description: Maintain ProcessDirect end point of custom error handling flow in case of custom error handling instead of standard error handling.
Change the default JMS queue to Q01 if you prefer to use the fully decoupled pipeline across all your IDoc scenarios (recommendation is to stick to X01, i.e., using the integrated messaging runtime).
Set parameter to true if you like to use custom error handling instead of standard error handling.
Change the prefix if you like to setup an additional pipeline.
Maintain the single point of entry which can be used across all your IDoc scenarios.
Switch parameter to false if you like to use the so called tilde option to determine the partner ID (not recommended).
Set parameter to true if you like to use custom exit across all scenarios.
Maintain ProcessDirect end point of global custom exit flow if you like to use custom exit across all scenarios.
